title: Motoring World - March 2016
description:
English | 166 pages | PDF | 22 MB

Motoring World is the auto magazine for the discerning auto enthusiast. It is for people who want not just numbers and by-the-book writing, but a real seat-of-the-pants experience when they open each page. For well over a decade, Motoring has provided readers cutting edge writing infused with wit and irreverence, top-notch photography and an approach that is entirely different from any other auto magazine. It is the only publication where you will find regular travel stories by road, stories on vintage and classic cars and bikes, unusual car vs bike comparison tests and many more such. We have it in our blood - and we're sure you do too
